responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "6AD1D856474C5E9777072595257D1ECC", "\"She doesn\'t like you to touch her equipment while she\'s working, and for good reason,\" Vagesh explained. \"A few of her mixtures reacted quite explosively when touched with flame.\" \"How old is she?\" I asked.\"I would guess about five.\" \"Five years?\" I asked, incredulously. \"Indeed. She is quite the prodigy,\" he said, beaming proudly. \"And quite resilient. I\'ve seen her ingest holly berry, mistletoe, even nightshade without betraying the slightest hint of discomfort. She does the majority of her alchemy experimentation using her senses of smell and taste. It\'s quite astonishing!\"")
